    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my reliable ride. It\u2019s been so well-taken care of and honestly runs like a dream! The interior is super clean, and it handles the road beautifully. Whether you're commuting or planning a weekend getaway, this car is totally ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love how it drives!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Equipped with the iconic S54B32 high-revving inline-six, this E46 M3 delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical configuration includes a variable M-differential lock and a chassis optimized for torsional rigidity. This unit has had the critical subframe reinforcement performed and the Double VANOS system overhauled, mitigating common platform weaknesses. It sits on a well-sorted suspension with refreshed bushings, providing the tactile feedback and balance that defined an era of performance engineering. Mechanically robust and aesthetically clean, it\u2019s a driver-focused example ready for the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean title. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained 2017 Audi S5 embodies the perfect balance of performance and daily usability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front fascia tell the story of spirited highway commutes. Inside, the Fine Nappa leather seats are supple and well-cared for, showing only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the Virtual Cockpit to the Bang & Olufsen sound system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle has been treated with the utmost care, boasting a comprehensive service history with recent fluid changes and a fresh set of tires. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers the confident grip of Quattro all-wheel drive. If you are looking for a reliable, high-performance coupe that has been loved but driven, this S5 is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a distinguished opportunity for the discerning driver. It exhibits a well-preserved aesthetic paired with a robust service history, ensuring consistent mechanical performance and reliability. Every aspect of this automobile reflects a commitment to quality, offering a sophisticated driving experience that surpasses standard market expectations. We invite you to experience the refined engineering and enduring value of this exceptional selection.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty ride and it has been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has always been super dependable for me, whether I'm just running errands or heading out on a road trip. It drives smoothly and has been well-loved, so it's totally ready for its next adventure with you! I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and see how great it feels behind the wheel. Drop me a message if you're interested!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s S54-powered masterpiece. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a linear power band that remains visceral up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including a comprehensive Vanos system refresh and structural reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, providing the precise turn-in and chassis feedback this platform is renowned for. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, its mechanical integrity and drivetrain performance are robust.",
      "price": 34500.0,
